at|mitche: Bidding:  Do you know what the "Notrump ladder" is?  
It shows the bids you make with varying strength hands of NT shape. 
With <15 points, open 1 of a suit and rebid 1NT.  
With 15-17 HCP, open 1NT.
With 18-19 HCP, open 1 of a suit and rebid 2NT over your partner's 1 level response. 
With 20-21 HCP, bid 2NT.
|
