nt||at|mitche:  With 22-24 HCP, bid 2@C followed by 2NT.
With 25-27 HCP, bid 2@C followed by 3NT. 
If you pick up more than 27 points, make sure it's a money game, open 2@C and jump to 4NT, natural. 
Responder will bid 1 extra level for each K or A she holds.
So the bidding was what it should have been.|
